data.description: Introducing this Beautiful 5 bedroom, 2 Story Home with a Finished Basement nestled in the desirable Glen at Widefield. Upon Arrival you'll be greeted by a well maintained exterior with a nice front porch. As you step inside the main level welcomes you with a open concept layout. A Spacious Living Room with Gas Fireplace, Main Level Office, A Modern Eat in Kitchen With All Appliances Included and Ample Granite Counters with Plenty of Space. The Upper Level has 4 Generous Size Bedrooms and a Loft providing ample space for everyone. The Large Master Suite is a True Retreat with a 5 Piece Bath featuring a Luxurious Soaking Tub, Seperate Shower, and Walk in Closet. Venture down to the Finished Basement, a versatile space ideal for a theater, recreation room, or even an additional living area. This extra space offers endless possibilities to cater to your lifestyle needs. This Area has a Large Family Room, Full Bathroom, and Additional 5th Bedroom.  Step Outside to the Large Fenced in Backyard. A Perfect Canvas to Make Your Own. You will find a Serene Area  Perfect for Outdoor Entertainment, Grilling on the Patio, and Relaxing Offering a great spot for Barbeques and Gatherings.  Easy Commute to all Military Bases, Shopping, Schools, Home Improvement Stores, and I25. This Beauty Shows Very Well and An Opportunity to Make and Cherish Memories. Pride in Ownership Shows.  Schedule Your Showing Today. You will not be disappointed. Great Home with Great Value ~
